Various scripts

GalleryDownloader - downloads images from the specified url and conditions (CSS selector, node attributes, etc.)
************
ImgOrientationFixer - Rotates JPG images in the given directory, according to their EXIF rotation (http://jpegclub.org/exif_orientation.html) and sets it to 1 (no rotation).
************
NuGetPack - Runs NuGet pack for all .csproj files which has corresponding (residing in the same directory) .nuspec file.
************
RunIf - Runs given executable if it is not already running.